le/.premium/netanyahu-dealt-israel-a-terrible-blow/0000018d-4c5b-d35c-a39f-ee5bdf4e0000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者在集会上援引大屠杀，要求释放被扣押在加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/protesters-invoke-holocaust-in-rallies-for-the-release-of-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018d-4cbe-d35c-a39f-eefe02710000</link><description>一千多名抗议者，其中包括被哈马斯在加沙扣押的人质的亲属，在特拉维夫所谓的人质广场和凯撒利亚总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的私人官邸外集会，要求立即释放人质</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 23:28:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/protesters-invoke-holocaust-in-rallies-for-the-release-of-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018d-4cbe-d35c-a39f-eefe02710000</guid></item><item><title>“我伴侣的死是对政府及其领导人的起诉”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/my-partners-death-is-an-indictment-against-the-government-and-its-leader/0000018d-4c71-d02c-a79f-4ffb02c50000</link><description>特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、海法都举行了推翻内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议活动，贝尔谢巴也是自 10 月加沙战争爆发以来首次举行抗议活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 20:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/my-partners-death-is-an-indictment-against-the-government-and-its-leader/0000018d-4c71-d02c-a79f-4ffb02c50000</guid></item><item><title>挑衅的国际法院法官称以色列-加沙战争是“政治性的”，在世界法院没有地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/defiant-icj-judge-says-gaza-war-with-israel-is-political-and-has-no-place-in-world-court/0000018d-4ba5-d561-a5bd-6faff0060000</link><description>法官朱莉娅·塞布廷德在提交给联合国最高法院的少数意见中表示，“南非没有证明”以色列在加沙的行为“具有必要的种族灭绝意图”，因此符合《种族灭绝公约》的规定</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 17:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/defiant-icj-judge-says-gaza-war-with-israel-is-political-and-has-no-place-in-world-court/0000018d-4ba5-d561-a5bd-6faff0060000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯坚持结束战争，以色列官员对人质协议持悲观态度</title><link>https://www.