质 ■ 内塔尼亚胡称人质抗议增加了哈马斯的要求，无助于努力 ■ 以色列国防军公布了加沙人高呼推翻政府的镜头哈马斯</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 03:35:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-live/yemens-houthis-say-they-attacked-a-british-ship-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-lebanon/0000018d-48c4-dc44-a5bf-c8f64edc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者找到了虐待巴勒斯坦牧羊人的新方法：让他们破产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-settlers-have-found-a-new-way-to-abuse-palestinian-shepherds-bankrupting-them/0000018d-4822-dc44-a5bf-c8b681660000</link><description>本周，警方扣押了 700 只羊，声称它们穿越了禁区。为了取回这些动物，牧羊人向定居者地区委员会支付了 150,000 谢克尔</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 00:21:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-settlers-have-found-a-new-way-to-abuse-palestinian-shepherds-bankrupting-them/0000018d-4822-dc44-a5bf-c8b681660000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列历史上最伟大的恐吓者”：内塔尼亚胡的恐吓策略如何操纵以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-one-generates-fear-like-him-how-netanyahus-scare-tactics-manipulate-israelis/0000018d-47c8-d02c-a79f-47db0d710000</link><description>乌里尔·阿布洛夫说，内塔尼亚胡权力的秘密在于滥用权力。作为恐惧政治的研究者，他试图理解我们如何才能爬出深渊，回到希望政治</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 23:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-one-generates-fear-like-him-how-netanyahus-scare-tactics-manipulate-israelis/0000018d-47c8-d02c-a79f-47db0d710000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称，他们被俘的儿子被哈马斯杀害。然后病理学家出现了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-26/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-their-captive-son-was-killed-by-hamas-then-a-pathologist-showed-up/0000018d-4756-d35c-a39f-ef5e4de10000</link><description>她的儿子被哈马斯扣为人质并在加沙被发现死亡，而对他尸体的尸检和有关他死亡的军方报告都没有结论，愤怒的马扬·谢尔曼要求以色列国防军和国家给出答案。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 