em><title>优先考虑人质的以色列人是真正理性的声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-who-prioritize-the-hostages-are-the-real-voice-of-reason/0000018d-467f-d02c-a79f-47ff7e620000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 17:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-who-prioritize-the-hostages-are-the-real-voice-of-reason/0000018d-467f-d02c-a79f-47ff7e620000</guid></item></channel></rss>